result.name: CD20+ T cells in Monoclonal B Cell Lymphocytosis and Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia
result.description: Quantification and phenotypic analysis of CD20+ T cells in MBL and CLL, and evaluation of the correlation of these phenotypic characteristics with disease features, particularly analysis of mutations in the TP53 gene from pathological B cells.
result.center: Centro Hospitalar e Universitario de Coimbra
